                        Get started
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="ml-3 inline-flex rounded-md shadow">
                    <a href="/schemes" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md text-white bg-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-800 transform transition duration-200 hover:scale-105">
